targets.query:
from(bucket: "TelemetryData")
  |> range(start: -500ms, stop: 0m)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "Formula1_measurements")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "wear_fl" or r["_field"] == "wear_fr" or r["_field"] == "wear_rl" or r["_field"] == "wear_rr" or r["_field"] == "wingDamage_fl" or r["_field"] == "wingDamage_fr")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["metric"] == "car")
  |> last()
  |> aggregateWindow(every: 500ms, fn: last, createEmpty: false)
